    TOP 10
    ActiveWBS
    ,CostCenter
    --,*

    ,Tags
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://s037costmgmt.dfs.core.windows.net/usage/exports/monthly/ACMMonthlyActualCost/202304*/Extended_ACMMonthlyActualCost_*.parquet',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) AS [result]
    where Tags is NULL --ActiveWBS <> CostCenter and
